Expected Error: demo to equal <jasmine.any(Buffer)>.

toBeRejectedWith
Expected a promise to be rejected with <jasmine.any(Buffer)> but it was rejected with Error: demo.

To be fair, that can be ameliorated with withContext somewhat:
expect(e).withContext("Expected a promise to be rejected with a different value").toEqual(jasmine.any(Buffer));
Expected a promise to be rejected with a different value: Expected Error: demo to equal <jasmine.any(Buffer)>.

